external_knowledge:
- Detailed information includes leave ID, leave type, start date, end date, purpose, user name, role, and department name; 
- User information includes user name and role; 
- Respective departments refer to the department names corresponding to each user.

- A 'Director' refers to a high-level manager in an organization; 
- 'Leave address' refers to the location where an employee will be during their approved leave; 
- 'Department' is implied by the 'leave_address' as different addresses may correspond to different departments within an organization.
